       </p>

      </div>
      <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA10d150n1-ptr" id="PJA10d150n1">1</a>
       
   <p>Congress adopted the resolutions regarding nonexportation on 7 and 8 Oct. 1774 (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Worthington C. Ford and others, eds., &lt;i&gt;Journals of the Continental Congress, 17741789&lt;/i&gt;, Washington, 19041937; 34 vols. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">JCC</span></span>, 1:5758), but see also a proposed resolution by <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> on the subject <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-02-02-0041-0003" class="document">[<ins title="editorial addition or explanation" class="ed">30 Sept. 1774</ins>]</a> (vol. 2:156157).</p>

